{"tid":186464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（八十後）5次劈炮自覺有型。做老細後鬧人唔受得氣。","createTime":"2017-04-04T08:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T23:56:45.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a182ba9ce298465de0a7d5e8a6f4da43b4e399","tid":186464,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">八十後的Cruz是廚師，最近五份工皆是裸辭</span>，對他來說如家常便飯。「細個係好囂架，我有才華，去到邊都請。」他大大小小的餐廳都做過，包括五星級香港W酒店、中環米芝蓮三星西餐廳。「辭職都係頂唔順公司制度或老闆要求。」<span style=\"color: red;\">他帶點自豪地說。<br />\r</span><br />\n\r<br />\n<br />\nCruz的裸辭故事類同：<br />\n<br />\n「好侮辱！炒完午餐，一脫圍裙我就走，好型。」<br />\n<br />\n「我米芝蓮三星，你俾翠華叉燒我？&hellip;係咪玩我？」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「返到香港實搵到第二份&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;。」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\n<br />\nCruz不想受氣，最終決定自己做老闆，<br />\n<br />\n兩個月前在旺角開設一間西餐廳，角色互換後即時指摘年輕一代&hellip;&hellip;、「我好彩啫，你都要食飯架？如果你行得出嚟個社會，咪接受一下社會囉。而家呢一代，唔係好受得氣。&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"28c79a507eb14c39d814afeedb5a83259323aac8","tid":186464,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5c2937d8bc7e4187dc39578a056313b0fca505","tid":186464,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"個名點讀"},{"pid":"c2b4c058264603b3b07af50061923426ca107321","tid":186464,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個名點讀</blockquote><br />\n照拼音讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca60ce185e6d0ac553d4ce08aa3b5b43ac85999","tid":186464,"uid":19542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個名點讀</blockquote><br />\n照拼音讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n括s"},{"pid":"37bd01e715b5d6cd191e87eebde76774d7c39729","tid":186464,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個名點讀</blockquote><br />\n照拼音讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n括s</blockquote><br />\n哽死？"},{"pid":"033ed15321f8e47ad0671319ec001216d9730979","tid":186464,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:59:51.000Z","msg":"屋企應該係有錢既?"},{"pid":"5aed3d0355972daba4e2d91a93f57680b97af856","tid":186464,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e40ee6c008c1e2867fadce60ed46eac0d37d05b","tid":186464,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"仆街死"},{"pid":"16312465033817badcefff719a93e13f6d847235","tid":186464,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:47:16.000Z","msg":"通常小氣既人唔受得氣 自己做老闆之後實起氣人受"},{"pid":"ae6f92a92487b5d96c47257f679b1f8a01cc2cf7","tid":186464,"uid":17268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T20:48:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"e9a49d2d7d121ba22e37631c22d00898c42760da","tid":186464,"uid":53728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T20:53:00.000Z","msg":"kr屈s"},{"pid":"e3d0f69ad9e35db7ba723d5e433a730e4bfe39cc","tid":186464,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:42:28.000Z","msg":"呢d真係垃撚圾"},{"pid":"a01d9b9d2b905f65a9928c638964e7135983c584","tid":186464,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:56:45.000Z","msg":"受過奶奶氣的家嫂，當佢做咗奶奶，就會去難為家嫂了"}]}